A: The problem statement asks you to find all pairs of points where the first point is on the upper left side of the second point, and there are no other points in the rectangle formed by the two points.
Here's a solution that uses a hashmap to keep track of the points that have been seen so far, and a counter to keep track of the number of pairs of points that satisfy the given condition:


class Solution {
    public int numberOfPairs(int[][] points) {
        // initialize the hashmap and the counter
        Map<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
        int count = 0;

        // iterate over all possible pairs of points
        for (int i = 0; i < points.length; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j < points.length; j++) {
                // check if the first point is on the upper left side of the second point
                if (points[i][0] < points[j][0] && points[i][1] > points[j][1]) {
                    // create a unique key for the pair of points
                    int key = points[i][0] * 10000 + points[i][1] * 100 + points[j][0] * 10 + points[j][1];
                    // check if the pair of points has already been seen
                    if (!map.containsKey(key)) {
                        // if not, add it to the hashmap and increment the counter
                        map.put(key, 1);
                        count++;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // return the counter
        return count;
    }
}

The code works by iterating over all possible pairs of points and checking if the first point is on the upper left side of the second point. If the pair of points satisfies this condition, it is added to the hashmap and the counter is incremented. The unique key for each pair of points is created by concatenating the coordinates of the points. This allows the code to detect duplicates and avoid counting them multiple times.

class Solution {
    public int numberOfSubstrings(String S) {
        char[] s = S.toCharArray();
        int n = s.length;
        int m = 0;
        int[] a = new int[n + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (s[i] == '0') {
                a[m++] = i;
            }
        }
        int tot1 = n - m;
        a[m] = n; // 哨兵
        int ans = 0;
        int i = 0; // >= left 的第一个 0 的下标是 a[i]
        for (int left = 0; left < n; left++) {
            if (s[left] == '1') {
                ans += a[i] - left; // 不含 0 的子串个数
            }
            for (int k = i; k < m; k++) {
                int cnt0 = k - i + 1;
                if (cnt0 * cnt0 <= tot1) {
                    break;
                }
                int cnt1 = a[k] - left - (k - i);
                ans += cnt1;
            }
            if (s[left] == '0') {
                i++; // 这个 0 后面不会再枚举到了
            }
        }
        return ans;
    }
}

